&lt;p&gt;LD34 Entry
Theme picked Two Button Control&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The game is about how a ball return to its owner from some post-apocalyptic ruins.
But you do not control the ball, you control other things in the environment.
Each level you control different things.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Or simply put, a adventure game with pinball gameplay&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is some end game cut scenes, so please try to beat the game:)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Controls:
Z and M
(R to reset the ball is struck somewhere unexpected)&lt;/p&gt;

